## ðŸŸ© Pattern 5: Large Hollow Rectangle

```
**********
*        *
*        *
**********
```

### âœ… Code:

```java
class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int rows = 4;
        int cols = 10;

        for (int i = 0; i < rows; i++) {
            for (int j = 0; j < cols; j++) {
                if (i == 0 || i == rows - 1 || j == 0 || j == cols - 1)
                    System.out.print("*");
                else
                    System.out.print(" ");
            }
            System.out.println();
        }
    }
}
```

